blocks.text: Olympic Gold Rush and Bodø/Glimt's Historic Champions League Night

Norway hunts double Olympic gold as Klaebo anchors the team sprint and the biathlon women chase relay glory. Then Bodø/Glimt welcome Inter Milan to Aspmyra for a landmark Champions League knockout debut.
⚽ Bodø/Glimt host Inter Milan in Champions League Round of 16 — 21:00
⚽ Arsenal travel to Wolves chasing top-four security — 21:00
